<div class="sub-content-header">Get Free Registration for Your Guests at CES</div>
<br />


        <img alt="" style="float: right;"  src="/images/content/Invite_Image_Web.jpg" />Free registration for the 2012 show ended on August 31, but as a CES exhibitor, you have the opportunity to offer your preferred guests and clients free registration up through the end of November 2011. Exhibitor invitations are one of the most cost effective methods of using the branding power of CES to promote your company’s presence at CES.<br />
        <br />
        New this year, starting in September, you will have the opportunity each month to download a series of banner advertisements in different sizes. These banners can be incorporated into your website or electronic messages promoting your presence at CES. These banners will link to a special registration page that gives your guests free registration for that designated month.<br />
        <br />
        With free registration ending one month earlier this year, we know that some of your preferred clients might have missed out on this great opportunity. Be their saviour! Your customers will love getting free advance registration (or reduced-rate on-site registration), and they will love that it came directly from you.<br />
        <br />
        <a  href="http://www.cesweb.org/exhibitors/sponsorships/freeOpps.asp#1925">Check out our Exhibitor Invitation page</a> to learn how you can download yours today.
    <br />
