<a name="5439"></a>

<div class="sub-content-header">Know Your Official Show Publications at CES</div>
<br />


        <img alt="" style="float: right;"  src="/images/content/2012Directory_Cover.jpg" />While there are a number of publications out there covering the day-to-day events of the International CES, there are only a few <strong>official</strong> show publications that guide our attendees and exhibitors through their CES experience. These publications <a  href="http://www.cesweb.org/exhibitors/sponsorships/printAdvertising.asp">offer prime advertising space</a> for companies like yours to reach thousands upon thousands of qualified consumer technology professionals, including executives, decision makers, buyers, distributors, engineers and a variety of other key audiences. <br />
        <br />
        These pieces include the Preshow Planner, Show Guide and Conference Brochure, the Official Show Directory and Official CES Daily, produced by TWICE. With more than 140,000 attendees, the value of these publications cannot be ignored and should be considered a critical component in any consumer technology company's advertising efforts. .
    <br />
