<div class="sub-content-header">Show The World Your Innovation!</div>
<br />


        <p><img width="101" height="150" alt="" style="margin-top: 0px; float: right; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px;"  width="101" height="150" src="/images/content/2K12Innovations_SAMPLE.jpg" />Call for Entries is now open! You know your product is the best. Does the rest of the world?<br />
        <br />
        As one of the most prestigious and respected awards in the consumer electronics industry, the CES Innovations Awards are a hallmark of the best-designed products in consumer technology. Products chosen as honorees enjoy instant recognition from consumers all over the world, as well as a front-and-center spotlight at CES.<br />
        <br />
        The International CES Innovations 2012 Design and Engineering Awards Call for Entries is now open. NEW for 2012, we've revamped the 30+ product categories and have introduced two brand new ones: Software &amp; Mobile Apps and Tablets, E-Readers &amp; Netbooks.<br />
        <br />
        Innovations honorees enjoy incredible opportunities, special recognition in the CE industry and worldwide exposure for your company, brands and products.<br />
        <br />
        The Call for Entries will remain open through September 16, 2011. <a  href="/awards/innovations/about.asp">Enter today</a>, and make sure you're not left behind! Questions? Contact us at <a  href="mailto:Innovations@CE.org">Innovations@CE.org</a>.</p>
