        <img alt="" style="float: right;"  src="/images/content/exhibitorschoiceawardlogo-140x200.jpg" />Last year's 2010 International CES® was named Favorite Show in Trade Show Exhibitors Association’s (TSEA) Exhibitor’s Choice Awards. CEA’s senior vice president of events and conferences, Karen Chupka, also was named TSEA’s Best Show Manager.<br />
